INSERT INTO `about` VALUES (1,'<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial;\">تطبيق أعرفي حقوقك</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">تم تأسيس هذا التطبيق في تاريخ 4 يوليو ٢٠١٦وهو الأول من نوعه في المملكة العربية السعودية ويهدف الى تعريف المرأة السعودية على كامل حقوقها بشكل عام وحقوقها في قضايا الأحوال الشخصية، مثل قضايا الحضانة، والطلاق، والنفقة</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\"> وهو يسهل للمرأة كيفية رفع الدعوى القضائية بنفسها والحصول على كامل حقوقها الشرعية والنظامية</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">يوفر التطبيق الخدمات التالية</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\"> معلومات قانونية مجانية للنساء -</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">استشارات قانونيه مختصره من خلال ايقونة </span><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">استشارة </strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">-</span></p>','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: &quot;SF UI Text&quot;;\">Know Your Rights</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">This application was developed on the 4th of July 2016, as the first of its kind in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. The application aims to explain all the legal rights of Saudi women in general and specifically their rights in family law matters, such as child custody, divorce and alimony lawsuits.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">The application facilitates the method of filing a judicial lawsuit by Saudi women themselves, as well as explaining all their Shariah and Regulatory rights.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">The application provides the following:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">1. Free legal information for women</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">2. Brief consultations through the icon: &quot;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Consultation</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">&quot;</span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Women are part of a society and their growth is part of a society’s prosperity. Sometimes women face difficulties in understanding their rights, so to help women understand their rights, I have established </span><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">“KNOW YOUR RIGHTS”</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\"> application on the 4th of July 2016. The application aims to facilitate, clarify, support and help women in knowing and understanding their Shariah and legal rights in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">“KNOW YOUR RIGHTS”</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\"> application is considered to be the first of its kind in Saudi Arabia and in the Middle East as it provides legal services and information. I personally and continuously work on the application to develop the content in conformity with the need of women.</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">About the Founder:</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Nasreen Alissa currently works as an attorney specialized in corporate law and she holds the following Degrees: </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Bachelor Degree in law from Nottingham University in Nottingham City </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Bachelor Degree in Sociology from the University of British Colombia in Vancouver City</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Master Degree in Law from City University in London </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Post Graduate Diploma in Law from City University in London </span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Message to all Saudi Females to Succeed: </strong></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">First</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Read 1 book a week</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Second</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Finish College</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Third</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Get a job</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Fourth</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Have a hobby that stimulates your mind</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Fifth</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Exercise, eat healthy, practice yoga and waking up early</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Sixth</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Surround yourself with friends who add value into your life</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Seventh</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Have a goal in life and pursue it</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Eighth</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Learn to to be independent</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Ninth</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Be careful who you trust</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Tenth</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: Lower your expectations to avoid unnecessary disappointments</span></p>','<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">المرأة هي جزء من المجتمع، ازدهارها من ازدهار المجتمع. أحيانا تواجه المرأة صعوبه للتعرف على حقوقها ورغبة مني في خدمة المجتمع ودعم المرأة قمت بتأسيس تطبيق اعرفي حقوقك في ٤ يوليو ٢٠١٦ م، وهو يهدف لتسهيل وتوضيح وشرح ودعم ومساعدة المرأة في معرفة حقوقها الشرعية والنظامية في المملكة العربية السعودية</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">تطبيق اعرفي حقوقك يعتبر التطبيق الأول من نوعه في المملكة العربية السعودية وعلى مستوى الشرق الأوسط حيث يوفر الخدمات والمعلومات القانونية، وأعمل عليه شخصياً وباستمرار لتطوير المحتوى بما يناسب حاجة المرأة</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">عن المؤسس</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">نسرين العيسى محامية متخصصة في مجال الشركات وهي حاصلة على الشهادات التالية</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">بكالوريوس قانون من جامعة نوتينقهام في مدينة نوتينقهام</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">بكالوريوس علم اجتماع من جامعة بريتش كولومبيا في مدينة فانكوفر</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">ماجستير قانون من جامعة سيتي ينيفيرستي في مدينة لندن</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">دبلوم عالي قانون من جامعة سيتي ينيفيرستي في مدينة لندن</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">رسالة الى جميع السعوديات للنجاح</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">أولا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: اقرئي كتاب كل اسبوع</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">ثانيا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: تخرجي من الجامعه</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">ثالثا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: توظفي</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">رابعا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: يجب أن يكون لديك هواية تغذي عقلك</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">خامسا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: مارسي الرياضة والغذاء الصحي واليوجا والاستيقاظ المبكر</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">سادسا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: كوني صداقات من النوع التي تضيف قيمة في حياتك</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">سابعا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: يجب أن يكون لك هدف في الحياه والسعي ورائه</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">ثامنا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: اعتمدي على نفسك</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">تاسعا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: كوني حذرة بمن تثقين بهم</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">عاشرا</strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">: لا تتوقعي شيئاً من أحد، وستري كل من حولك بصورة أجمل لأن أغلب خيبات الأمل تأتي بسبب ارتفاع سقف التوقعات</span></p>','<p><strong style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt;\">Terms and Conditions:</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Your access and use of the electronic application “Know Your Rights” is subject to the following terms and conditions in addition to the laws and regulations of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Your access to the application shall mean that you agree to these terms and conditions. By accessing, using and navigating the application, you will accept, without any constrain or condition, the terms and conditions of use stated in this document.</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt;\">Amendment of the Terms and Conditions</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">“Know Your Rights” shall have the right to amend these terms and conditions, provided that a notification on the amendments made to this page shall be published.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">The amendments shall enter into force as soon as they are made unless provided otherwise. Your frequent use of the application after such amendments means that you agree to such amendments. You should undertake periodic visits to this page to revise the current terms and conditions of use.</span></p><p><strong style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt;\">Conduct</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;\">You agree to access and use the application for legitimate purposes only. You shall be fully liable for knowledge and action of any and all of the laws and regulations, rules and provisions related to your use of the application. Upon accessing the application, you agree to refrain from the following: </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt;\">1-To use the application for the purpose of committing a crime or to encourage others to get involved in any act which might be considered a crime or involves a civil liability. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 1